data.description: Introducing a charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath house located in the quaint town of Clinton, TN with no restrictions or an HOA.  This residence has been updated throughout to offer a comfortable and inviting living space. The exterior features vinyl windows and metal siding, which not only adds to its aesthetic appeal but also contributes to low maintenance and energy efficiency. As you approach the property, you will notice the well maintained level yard providing a perfect setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Step inside and you will be greeted by the welcoming atmosphere created by recent renovations while keeping the home's original charm. Another appealing aspect of this home is the proximity to schools, making it an excellent choice for families with children. Additionally, the home's location near the quaint town of Clinton adds to its peaceful and serene charm. Take advantage of the towns unique allure by exploring local shops, enjoying hospitality of cozy restaurants, or taking leisurely walks through its picturesque downtown streets. You'll love being part of a tight-knit community that embodies the essence of small town living. Buyer to verify all information.
